OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773662582
OL,3,CTeenager suffers slash wound in knife
OL,4,Cfight outside supermarket
OL,6,FTwo teenagers have been arrested after
OL,7,Fa 17-year-old suffered a slash wound
OL,8,Fin a knife fight outside a supermarket
OL,9,Fin a Nottinghamshire town.
OL,11,FPolice were called to Asda on
OL,12,FPriestsic Road in Sutton-in-Ashfield
OL,13,Fjust before noon on Friday 13 March to
OL,14,Freports of violence involving weapons.
OL,16,FThe 17-year-old was taken to hospital
OL,17,Fwith a slash injury to his arm along
OL,18,Fwith a 24-year-old man who had an
OL,19,Finjury to his elbow.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
