CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773662582
OL,3,CTeenager suffers slash wound in knife
OL,4,Cfight outside supermarket
OL,6,FA third victim, a 23-year-old man,
OL,7,Falso suffered an injury to his arm.
OL,9,FPolice have arrested two 16-year-old
OL,10,Fboys on suspicion of causing grievous
OL,11,Fbodily harm with intent who are being
OL,12,Fheld in custody.
OL,14,FDetective Sergeant Adam Penn, of
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "We do
OL,16,Fnot tolerate violence or those who
OL,17,Fthink it is acceptable to carry or use
OL,18,Fweapons.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
