OL,3,CTeenager suffers slash wound in knife
OL,4,Cfight outside supermarket
OL,6,F"Following these arrests we continue
OL,7,Fto investigate this incident and
OL,8,Fefforts are ongoing to trace other
OL,9,Fpeople believed to have been involved.
OL,11,F"If anyone has information about those
OL,12,Finvolved who has not yet spoken with
OL,13,Fus, please call 101 quoting incident
OL,14,F868 of 13 March, or speak with
OL,15,FCrimestoppers if you wish to remain
OL,16,Fanonymous."
